{"prompt": "Generate a website for a AI startup. The website should be sophisticated and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>InnovateAI</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e50914; /* Red brand color */\n            --secondary-color: #f4f4f4;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #cccccc;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.8), rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.5)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/e50914/ffffff?text=AI+Innovation') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .container h2 {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #cccccc;\n            color: #e50914;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons (optional, but good for features) -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>InnovateAI</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#features\">Features</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Transforming Tomorrow with Intelligent Solutions</h2>\n        <p>We leverage cutting-edge artificial intelligence to drive innovation and empower businesses.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About InnovateAI</h2>\n        <p>At InnovateAI, we are a team of passionate researchers and engineers dedicated to pushing the boundaries of artificial intelligence. Our mission is to develop sophisticated AI solutions that solve complex problems, enhance efficiency, and unlock new possibilities across various industries. We believe in the power of AI to shape a better future.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Core Capabilities</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"></i>\n                <h3>Machine Learning</h3>\n                <p>Advanced algorithms for predictive analytics, pattern recognition, and intelligent automation.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-brain\"></i>\n                <h3>Deep Learning</h3>\n                <p>Cutting-edge neural networks for complex data analysis, natural language processing, and computer vision.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-cogs\"></i>\n                <h3>AI Integration</h3>\n                <p>Seamless integration of AI technologies into your existing systems for enhanced performance.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Ready to Innovate?</h2>\n        <p>Discover how InnovateAI can revolutionize your business operations and strategies.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get in Touch</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <p>&copy; 2024 InnovateAI. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@innovateai.com\">info@innovateai.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll to section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}